title.en: Itsuwari no Seijo wa Ryuukoku no Mahoutsukai ni narimashita
Ane no Migawari de Konyaku shitara Naze ka Henkyou no Seijo to Yobareru you ni narimashita
Higeki no Heroine Buru Imouto no Sei de Konyaku Hakishita no desu ga, Naze ka Seigikan no Tsuyoi Outaishi ni Karamareru you ni narimashita
Sabaku no Kuni no Amefurashi Hime ~Zense de Shokei Sareta Mahoutsukai wa Nouka no Musume ni Narimashita~
Zense Seijo datta Watashi wa Kusushi ni narimashita
Yomei Wazuka Dakara to Tsuihou sareta Seijo desu ga, Junrei no Tabi ni Detara Chou Kenkou ni Narimashita
Kusuri de Osanaku Natta Okage de Reikoku Koushaku-sama ni Hirowaremashita - Suterare Seijo wa Renkinjutsushi ni Modorimasu
Kyuutei Mahou-shi Kubi ni Nattande, Inaka ni Kaette Mahou-ka no Sensei ni Narimasu
Watashi wa Nise Seijo Rashii no de, Kyuutei wo Dete Ringoku de Kurashimasu
Akuyaku Seijo no Yarinaoshi - Enzai de Shokeisareta Seijo wa Oshi no Eiyuu wo Sukuu Tame ni Gaman wo Yamemasu
Senjou no Seijo ~Imouto no Kawari ni Koushaku Kishi ni Totsugu Koto ni narimashita ga, Ima wa Shiawase desu~
Seijo ni Naritai Wake de wa Arimasen ga Henkyou kara Kita Inaka Musume nanoni Ou Taishi-hi Kouho ni Erabarete Shimaimashita!?
Itsuwari no Inaka Reijou, Osananajimi no Ouji-sama wo Kouryaku-chuu
Iekara Nigedashitai Watashi ga, Ukkari Akogare no Daimahoutsukai-sama wo Katteshimattara
